{"tid":85424,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣（14）ちょとお 聞いてる","createTime":"2017-01-18T10:10:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-01T06:05:30.000Z","uid":21274,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e3baa5b95a8dc840f05cac19aaf8a34c5ae4ae90","tid":85424,"uid":21274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:10:55.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><blockquote>想追返前post請善用搜尋功能&quot;新垣結衣 (X)&quot;<br />\n2樓新劇資訊，3樓綜藝/相關影片、資訊<br />\n4樓新手入門攻略、常見問題、相集<br />\n長都要睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 爬晒先好黎問野</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">2017新年快樂</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://s23.postimg.org/awsg6jk8b/IMG_0162.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs23.postimg.org%2Fawsg6jk8b%2FIMG_0162.jpg&h=b085e54d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>秋季新劇：《逃避雖可恥但有用》</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CsPghtrVMAA-YH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCsPghtrVMAA-YH5.jpg&h=1a00743c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">官網：<a href=\"http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.tbs.co.jp%2FNIGEHAJI_tbs%2F&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=db7ba5f0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.tbs.co.jp/NIGEHAJI_tbs/</a><br />\nFB：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fnigehaji.tbs%2F&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=413569fd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/nigehaji.tbs/</a><br />\nTwitter：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fnigehaji_tbs%2F&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=6995bedc\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/nigehaji_tbs/</a><br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fnigehajigram%2F&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=fb8fb2d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/nigehajigram/</a><br />\n預告片：<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nM2MAx6_65Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DnM2MAx6_65Y&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=0afcc926\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nM2MAx6_65Y</a><br />\n出演：<br />\n新垣結衣/星野源/大谷亮平/藤井隆<br />\n真野惠里菜/成田凌/山賀琴子/宇梶剛士<br />\n富田靖子/古田新太/石田百和子<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/14/233547_f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F14%2F233547_f50f852bf9aab8e759504ba6f724920d.gif&h=44cdcd3a&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/10/15/185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F10%2F15%2F185308_aad906a54864ad5e19c4c7c30c6216d2.gif&h=b1ff0dd8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n主題曲：星野 源 - 「恋」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhOVibLEDhA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DjhOVibLEDhA&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=7c8edf7f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=jhOVibLEDhA</a><br />\n恋ダンス 教學片<br />\n<a href=\"http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMOyGxzG91yo&d=aZ%2BvH1YulBJsRS0Mk%2FwPpgT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=478339a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://youtu.be/MOyGxzG91yo</a></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><br />\n<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCsPUakUVMAEaIm9.jpg&h=ff57ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/CufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FCufWpTsXgAE8r5D.jpg&h=e6f7af0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n</div><br />\n女星新垣結衣接拍十月開播TBS日劇《逃避雖可恥但有用》，飾演像上班一樣為特定目的結婚的新妻，劇集根據海野津波在月刊《Kiss》連載的同名漫畫改編，以&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的價值觀為基礎，講述契約結婚的主人公的故事。<br />\n  劇中新垣結衣飾演主人公森山，這位25歲愛妄想的女子沒有男友，畢業後沒有工作，做派遣職員沒公司用，生活不順終日煩惱，她幫單身職員津崎做家務，對方提出不如像上班一樣結婚，於是他們秘密定下契約，開始了&ldquo;丈夫是雇主，妻子是職員&rdquo;的新婚生活。<br />\n  原作者海野津波說：&ldquo;<span style=\"color: red;\">還沒確定日劇化的時候，我就和朋友們幻想過真人版的演員，當時還說如果讓新垣結衣演森山怎麼樣，如果她主演的話絕對能拿滿分，聽說日劇版真的是新垣結衣主演我特別開心。</span>&rdquo;<br />\n  制作人那須田淳說：&ldquo;剛讀原著的時候，主人公契約結婚和新婚愛情生活之間巧妙的關聯讓我感覺很有趣，主題非常能引起現代人的共鳴。<span style=\"color: red;\">我認為有幽默感又有表現力的新垣結衣是這個角色的最佳人選，一定能把歡笑和勇氣傳達給觀眾。</span>&rdquo;制作人宮崎真佐子說：&ldquo;因為契約結婚而一起生活的兩位主人公的關系很有趣，觀眾應該比較容易帶入感情，工作和結婚是現在很重要的社會問題。也許很多人都有誰真的需要自己這樣的煩惱，劇中會有詳細的描寫"},{"pid":"c3c805d6154547ef1a48faae1fc7538f9fcc1801","tid":85424,"uid":74283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:28:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vbscxe5g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvbscxe5g&h=e8a7eeaa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ntest"},{"pid":"1b7a5be02bd5ac1aef04f4aa2cf49d57da52f40e","tid":85424,"uid":46688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3fc1366b3eae424e1b8644f8f765d15bb1f5d97","tid":85424,"uid":2857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10778fe5617c6a31b6e56305ca4e9779565345dd","tid":85424,"uid":35248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"又爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"502b20c33e8d0ea4db0fd71e7afd4111deeb60c8","tid":85424,"uid":34156,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T10:45:41.000Z","msg":"追唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3487146ea4313026a0308e146f0225ed2f089d67","tid":85424,"uid":2801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>追唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n一早放棄了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n留名算 爆得太快<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a75fe021493cb907ce9d278588d800a6c444ce0","tid":85424,"uid":37070,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T11:53:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b89016c64d9ed0cb7834163742e9a9bfb81d9db8","tid":85424,"uid":56758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:49:55.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n逃恥入坑<br />\n今日子睇到第五集<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c63fa3c1dbf1e384b63f9aee76e8c37d94e6e45f","tid":85424,"uid":37543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:55:50.000Z","msg":"點解又開多個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f959a20e56dd59bd83e3ab09d09b0990db8c6f28","tid":85424,"uid":48536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T12:59:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/18/205856_c008b9d5391425802a575397184f6170.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F18%2F205